<title type="html"><![CDATA[12/23 (Thu.) mental health/ impromptu speech (Host: Lawrence)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=574&amp;p=597#p597"><![CDATA[
Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40: Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />We will hold a hybrid meeting on Thursday:<br /><br />On-site meeting:<br />If you have received at least one dose of vaccine, please join our physical meeting:<br />Dante coffee 丹堤 臺北市大安區濟南路三段25號 忠孝新生 MRT Exit 3<br /><br />On-line meeting:<br />If you haven’t gotten any vaccine or live far away from Taipei, please join our online meeting:<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ... <br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br />Session 1, mental health<br />Emotion plays an important part in our health.<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.betterhealth.vic.gov.au/health/healthyliving/negative-emotions">https://www.betterhealth.vic.gov.au/hea ... e-emotions</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1, Do you have any negative emotion? What? Why? Share one that happened recently. <br />2, How do you think negative emotion affect your body, mind and spirit? Share your experience. <br />3, What do you usually do to keep a healthy mind and mood?<br />4, If you have any friend, family member, colleague who often give you negative energy, what would you do?<br /><br />Session 2 ‘impromptu discussion + impromptu speech’ <br />For impromptu discussion time (40 minutes), each person prepares one or two questions for the small group discussion.<br />For impromptu speech time (20 minutes), the host will pick some people to answer his questions. The purpose of impromptu speech (Table topic) is to train the speaker to give a speech without any preparation. <br />Speaking time will be strictly controlled. Each answer is for 2 minutes.<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.丹堤咖啡有100元低消喔!<br />2.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />3.請帶著開放的心與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=89">AndrewWang</a> — Fri Dec 17, 2021 9:44 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
